How to update
+++++++++++++

  * git clone https://github.com/Lora-net/LoRaMac-node.git
  * cd LoRaMac-node
  * git checkout master
  * Replace the necessary files in LoRaMac-node/src/radio and LoRaMac-node/src/mac folders
  * Ensure that the CMakeLists and Kconfig files match the new version of the LoRaMac-node

The following folders are used in this library:

+-------------------------+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| LoRa-Mac                | Zephyr                      | Comments                                                     |
+-------------------------+-----------------------------+--------------------------------------------------------------+
| LoRaMac-node/src/radio  | ext/lib/lorawan/mac         | Contains LoRaMAC layer                                       |
+-------------------------+-----------------------------+--------------------------------------------------------------+
| LoRaMac-node/src/mac    | ext/lib/lorawan/radio       | Contains LoRaMAC radios                                      |
+-------------------------+-----------------------------+--------------------------------------------------------------+

